OL,5, The widow of a top Scottish government 
OL,6, official, who died after contracting   
OL,7, Covid, believes the full details of his
OL,8, illness were concealed to protect the  
OL,9, reputation of a troubled hospital.     
OL,11,FAndrew Slorance went into Glasgow's    
OL,12,FQueen Elizabeth University Hospital for
OL,13,Fcancer treatment a year ago.           
OL,15,FHis wife Louise believes he caught     
OL,16,FCovid there as well as another         
OL,17,Flife-threatening infection.            
OL,19,FThe health board said it had been "open
OL,20,Fand honest".                           
